---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About CorpX Technologies">
  <section class="mt-16 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About CorpX Technologies</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-12">
      Aligning Innovation with Deliverable Optimism Since 2008.
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-12 text-left max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Our Story</h2>
        <p>
          Founded during the early waves of digital transformation, CorpX Technologies quickly positioned itself as a leader in scalable ambiguity and stakeholder-driven deliverable ecosystems.
          We've survived multiple market shifts, leadership changes, and rebranding efforts without fundamentally altering our commitment to quarterly metrics and buzzword optimization.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Our Mission</h2>
        <blockquote class="italic border-l-4 border-blue-900 pl-4 text-gray-600">
          "To deliver consistent, scalable, right-sized solutions by dynamically empowering a resilient, cross-functional future."
        </blockquote>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Our Vision</h2>
        <p>
          We envision a future where organizations embrace continuous iterative resilience, fueled by stakeholder alignment frameworks and dynamically pivoted innovation strategies.
          At CorpX, the future isn’t just unwritten — it’s actively rescheduled.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Our Values in Action</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li><strong>Optimistic Agility:</strong> Move fast. Realign faster.</li>
          <li><strong>Scalable Empathy:</strong> Listen carefully to feedback we cannot act on.</li>
          <li><strong>Data-Driven Alignment:</strong> Craft metrics that support whatever the leadership decision was.</li>
          <li><strong>Courageous Resilience:</strong> Survive initiatives you never signed up for.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-16">
      <a href="/careers" class="bg-blue-900 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-md text-lg font-bold hover:bg-blue-700 transition">
        Join Us
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
